lead_paragraph: James Paxton had maybe the best start of his young career Sunday. In even better news for the Seattle Mariners, he's doing well after taking a line drive off his pitching arm.

headline.print_headline: Paxton's Gem Ends in Scary Moment, Mariners Beat Angels 3-1
